## 1. Overall Save Format
- Plain JSON (SaveFileVersion: 20)
- Top-level keys of interest:
  - `IslandManager.islands[]`
  - `ResourceManager.GlobalResources.Resources[]` → current stocks
  - `ResearchManager.CompletedResearchTimes[]` → `{key: ID, value: level}`
  - `PopulationManager.PopulationTiers[]` → consumption
  - `RouteManager.routes[]` → trade routes
  - `GameEntities[]` inside each island

## 2. Production / Consumption Data (the core you already solved)
Every production/consumption value lives at:

`IslandManager.islands[X].GameEntities[Y].components[Z].internalstorage`

Inside `internalstorage`:
- `OutputResources.Resources[]` → production (key = resource ID, value.balance = raw amount per cycle)
- `InputResources.Resources[]` → consumption (same format)

